embeds.title: Thank you for visiting Non-Partisan Delaware
embeds.description:
Thank you for visiting Non-Partisan Delaware.

Our bot automatically prunes Guests daily who have been inactive for more than 7 days without completing our onboarding process.  You are welcome to [rejoin at any time](https://discord.gg/j5nRAFZEuZ) if you have additional questions, and may complete the onboarding process at that time to avoid being pruned again in the future.

embeds.title: REMINDER: Complete Onboarding
embeds.description: Prospective members of Non-Partisan Delaware who wish to be considered for full membership, or who just want to be added to our contact lists to receive updates from NPD, must complete the Onboarding Process in $$onboardingChannel$$.  Guests who do not complete Onboarding will be removed after 7 days of inactivity.

embed.title: Donate to Non-Partisan Delaware!
embed.description:
You can donate to Non-Partisan Delaware through [PayPal](https://paypal.me/NonPartisanDE).

We also accept checks delivered in person or mailed to:
*Non-Partisan Delaware*
*PO Box 1021*
*Dover, DE 19903*

We are also permitted under Delaware Campaign Finance laws to receive donations of less than $100 in cash.

We *__**deeply**__* appreciate your support!

Thank you,
